<H2>Subscriptions</H2>

As of May, 2002 subscriptions are $39 per year (four issues) for ACM
Members, $34 per year for ACM Student Members, and $164 for nonmembers. An
electronic subscription is $31 for members, $27 for student members, and
$131 for non-members. A combined print and online subscription is $47 for
ACM Members, $41 for ACM Student Members, and $197 for nonmembers. You
can subscribe by:
<UL>
<li><A HREF="http://www.acm.org/catalog/journals/109.html"> the web</A>
<li>calling 1-800-342-6626 (outside the U.S., 1-212-626-0500), or
<li>sending e-mail to <A
	HREF="mailto:colon[]acmhelp@acm.org"><TT>acmhelp@acm.org</TT></A> (or
	<TT><A
	HREF="mailto:colon[]acm_europe@acm.org">acm_europe@acm.org</A></TT>).
</ul>

<H2>Acquiring Individual Articles</H2>

All past articles published in ACM :journalAcronym[] are available through the 
<A HREF="http://portal.acm.org/browse_dl.cfm?linked=1&part=transaction&idx=J777&coll=portal&dl=ACM">ACM Portal (:journalAcronym[] gateway)</a> and the
<A HREF="http://www.lib.washington.edu/rss/acm.html">ACM Article 
Delivery Service</A>.

<H2>Single Copies of Issues</H2>
Single copies are $18 each to ACM members and $40 to nonmembers.
For credit card orders (MasterCard, VISA,
American Express) in the US and Canada, call toll tree 1-800-342-6626.
From New York or outside the US and Canada: 212-626-0500.

Alternatively, in North America, please send order your order to one 
of the following addresses.
<UL>
Postal mail:colon[]
<UL>
ACM Order Department<br> 
RO. Box 12114<br>
Church Street Station<br>
New York, NY 10257<br>
</UL>
<br>
Fax:colon[] 212-944-1318  
<br>
E-mail:colon[] <A href=mailto:colon[]acmhelp@acm.org>acmhelp@acm.org</A>
</UL>

In Europe you may use one of the following contact addresses.
<UL>
